<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA23">
<l>taḻumpirunta cārṅkanāṇ ṭōyntavā maṅkai</l>
<l>taḻumpirunta tāḷcakaṭañ cāṭit – taḻumpirunta</l>
<l>pūṅkōtai yāḷveruvap poṉpeyarōṉ mārpiṭanta</l>
<l>vīṅkōta vaṇṇar viral</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Scarred were  the palms that had touched the Śārṅga bow string,</l>
<l>scarred were the feet, having kicked the cart, scarred were</l>
<l>the fingers of him the colour of the swelling flood who dug into the chest</l>
<l>of him named after gold, so that she with the flower garland  was frightened.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
